The lowest cost Trading App with the most advance technology and features.
DC trading application developed by PT. Deu Calion Futures (DC Futures).

Stable and Innovative Trading Platforms
DC Webtrader: DC Webtrader is a one-stop trading platform. Best features in integrating quotes, charts, transactions, analysis and report. Access global markets and transact from any browser.
DC Mobile App: Best solutions for any trading needs of transaction, features, news and trend. Available on Google Play and App Store.
DC Desktop: Created with the most advanced application management features to help you control your trading positions efficiently. Available on Windows and MacOS.
MetaTrader 4 (MT4): Start trading transactions in MT4 by integrating your DC account login server name and password in MT4.

Security of Funds.
BAPPEBTI's policy requires that Client's funds are stored in a Segregated Account. DC Futures only uses a Margin Deposit Bank that has been registered in BAPPEBTI.
Deposit & Withdrawal
Fast and secure process for deposits and withdrawals! Deposits and Withdrawals can only be made on your name. Third party transfers are prohibited.
Minimum deposit: $200 (No fees charged)
Minimum withdrawal: $10.


Negative Balance Protection

Volatility often occurs in the market. DC policy provide a negative balance protection for clients.

Risk Management
The Company continually identifies, asses, and monitors each type of risk associated with its operations and assessing the effectiveness of the policies, arrangements, and procedures in place.
DC Futures Instruments:
Various choice of instruments on DC online trading platform.
Forex: Available more than 25 Major/Minor Currency Pairs in the most competitive spreads starting from 0.0 pips.
Metal: Gold & Silver
Futures: Access to International STOCK INDEX and Oil transactions with competitive spread facilities and low margin requirements.
Stock: International Stock Buy and Sell Transactions such as Facebook, Amazon, Apple and many more with low commission starting from 0.4%.

Fixed spread starts from 0,8 pips in Forex
